Name: SL Track Jumping and Flipping
Author: Vials
Notes: Practice tracking against super fast, jumping targets. Work on your flip timing.

Name: Magik tank shredder
Author: Vials
Notes: Kill as many tanks as possible using your abilities.

Name: Are you nuts?!
Author: Vials
Notes: Do your best to nut flying targets with squirrel. You can use your abilities, including traps.

Name: SL Anti-Fly Abilities
Author: Vials
Notes: Practice managing your abilities to maximize your damage output and take down evasive flying targets.

Name: Trident, Trident, Again-dent?
Author: Vials
Notes: Practice leading flying targets with Namor's tridents. No abilities, just dial in your left clicks.

Name: Hawk-high Ground
Author: Vials
Notes: Press start, then take the jump pad to your right to get up to high ground. Focus on landing as many headshots as possible while staying on height.
